-Th%C3%B4i-th%E1%BA%ADp-tam-b%C3%ACnh-s%E1%BB%B1-C%C3%B4ng-Ph%E1%BB%A5/poem-fRK8CGJbo3SFane4NSBj2A">Tặng Thôi thập tam bình sự Công Phụ - 贈崔十三評事公輔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-fZekov0n38p16zJzIaCBWA">Thu dạ hoài ngâm - 秋夜懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-tam-t%E1%BB%AD-Thi%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A1/poem-0xk1QF8_Aqf5qUjE6ECGKA">Thương đệ tam tử Thiên Hoá - 傷第三子天化</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-thu%E1%BB%B7-khi%E1%BB%83n-ho%C3%A0i/poem-fJ7dsvdhURP9WS38n6MV1g">Thướng thuỷ khiển hoài - 上水遣懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
